Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
get_capacitance_unit(25.10)                        get_capacitance_unit(25.10)

Name
       get_capacitance_unit

Syntax
       get_capacitance_unit

       Returns  the  capacitance unit (in picofarads) for the current session,
       which may be derived from the library file or set with the setLibraryU-
       nit -cap parameter.. This unit will be used  while  generating  reports
       and for constraint settings.

Example
       The following command returns the session capacitance unit:

       get_capacitance_unit

       1.000000pf

